history.speaker: interviewer
history.text: Hello John Smith, thanks for joining us today to discuss the Senior Python Developer position at our company. Could you start by telling me a bit about yourself and why you're interested in this role?

history.speaker: interviewer
history.text: Could you walk me through your approach to debugging a complex issue in a large codebase?

history.speaker: interviewer
history.text: How do you ensure the code you write is maintainable and can be understood by other team members?
